AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1079 House Bill No. 871*
by inserting the following new subsection at the end of SECTION 1:
(c) A third-party lender has no liability with respect to the use or return of
deposits described in subsection (b) or determining whether an appropriate form of
security was obtained for the use of the deposited funds unless the third-party lender
takes ownership or control of the condominium project through foreclosure or other
remedy, and only then to the extent of any deposits not already disbursed and
expended.
